OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1783939847
OL,3,CWater supply warning for parts of
OL,4,CHerefordshire due to hot weather
OL,6,FPeople in parts of Herefordshire are
OL,7,Fbeing warned of water supply issues
OL,8,Fdue to the hot weather.
OL,10,FWelsh Water says areas including
OL,11,FKingsthorne, St Owen Cross, Upton
OL,12,FBishop, Wormelow, Old Gore and the
OL,13,FLinton area of Ross-on-Wye are having
OL,14,Fproblems.
OL,16,FIt says people might experience low
OL,17,Fpressure or intermittent supply due to
OL,18,Fhigh demand because of the hot
OL,19,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
