OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1783939847
OL,3,CWater supply warning for parts of
OL,4,CHerefordshire due to hot weather
OL,6,FIt has apologised for any
OL,7,Finconvenience cause and says further
OL,8,Fupdates will be released as it gets
OL,9,Fmore information.
OL,11,FPaul English, the Licencee at the
OL,12,FKings Head Ducklow, said they have
OL,13,Fbeen having problems with water supply
OL,14,Ffor around 10 days, especially between
OL,15,F7pm and 10pm in the evening.
OL,17,FIt has been causing so many problems
OL,18,Fthat they have had to buy bottled
OL,19,Fwater to flush the toilets and have
OL,20,Fhad to buy in cans of drink as their
OL,21,Fpumps for fizzy drinks aren't working.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
