PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1783939847
OL,3,CWater supply warning for parts of
OL,4,CHerefordshire due to hot weather
OL,6,FPaul says this is the "worst he has
OL,7,Fever seen" the water supply and they
OL,8,Fare having to be creative to avoid it
OL,9,Fclosing them down at times.
